<b>Subject:</b> PvP class<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/datel.gif" width=46 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dateblnk.gif" width=100 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dater.gif" width=306 height=22 border=0></center><BR></STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#F4D99F FACE=arial>
<P>Which class do you think is the best at PvP? Not in a group situation, but one on one (pets allowed). I have heard that the warrior is basically useless against a caster because all they have to do is root him and he's finished, is this true? Or is it hard for someone to root another player of the same level? I realize there is no best class who will beat every other class hands down, but I also know that some classes aren't very well suited for PvP.

</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
